{"word":"Haran","slug":"haran","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Haran</b> <a href=\"#/H2039\">H2039</a><br/><a href=\"#/H2771\">H2771</a> <br/> 1. Father of Lot and brother of Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=31'>Gen 11:31</a><br/> 2. Son of Caleb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=46'>1Ch 2:46</a><br/> 3. A Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=9'>1Ch 23:9</a><br/> 4. Called also Charran<br/> - A place in Mesopotamia to which Terah and Abraham migrated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=31'>Gen 11:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=5'>Gen 12:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=4'>Act 7:4</a> <br/> - Death of Terah at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=32'>Gen 11:32</a> <br/> - Abraham leaves by divine command<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=5'>Gen 12:5</a> <br/> - Jacob flees to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=43'>Gen 27:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=7'>Gen 28:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29'>Gen 29</a> <br/> - Jacob returns from, with Rachel and Leah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=21'>Gen 31:21</a> <br/> - Conquest of, by king of Assyria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=19&verse=12'>2Ki 19:12</a> <br/> - Merchants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=23'>Eze 27:23</a> <br/> - Idolatry in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=2'>Jos 24:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=14'>Jos 24:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=37&verse=12'>Isa 37:12</a> "}]}